h4. Actor:
Administrator.

h4. Description:
Name of use case represents its functionality.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [Project Track|guide:_ShowProjectTrackPlugin] option from top menu bar.
* Click "Settings" sub menu from left menu.
* Click *Project* link.
* [Show Landing Page of "System Project"|guide:ShowPtProjectActionService].
* Select a Line-Item from grid view.
* Click "Edit" button from tool bar.
* Open *System Project* in Edit Mode.

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "Select Project of Project track" privilege.

h4. Process:
* Get *System Project* details from server.

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** Show selected *System Project* information in input form.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].
